        </text><text class="left_indent_0 first_line_indent_24">You are therefore required, without prejudice
            to your other duties under this or any other Ordinance, under <ref>section 73(2)</ref>
            of the Ordinance, not to commit any act which is [an unlawful discriminatory act
                under<i> (insert reference to relevant Part of provision of the Ordinance)</i>] [an
            unlawful act of harassment under <i>(insert reference to relevant Part or provision of
                the Ordinance)</i>] [a contravention of <ref>section 41</ref> of the Ordinance] [a
            contravention of <ref>section
                42</ref>/<ref>43</ref>/<ref>44</ref>/<ref>45</ref>/<ref>46</ref>/<ref>47</ref> of
            the Ordinance by reference to <ref>Part 3</ref>/<ref>Part 4</ref> of the
            Ordinance].<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></text><text class="left_indent_0 first_line_indent_24">If compliance with the above requirement
